Package asreml.input

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsremlAsd
    Asreml .asd file is an Asreml data file.
    AsremlColumn
    The Class AsremlColumn is used to define columns in the ASREML command file and the columns information such as flags and factors.
    AsremlColumns
    The Class AsremlColumns is used to store a collection of AsremlColumn s.
    AsremlErrorVariance
    Class used to define extra variance structures from blup analysis
    AsremlErrorVariances
    The Class AsremlErrorVariances is used to store a collection of AsremlErrorVariance
    AsremlFixedEffect
    The Class FixedEffect is used to define fixed effect in the ASREML command file
    AsremlFixedEffects
    The Class FixedEffects is used to store a collection of AsremlFixedEffect s.
    AsremlGrm
    Class to define writing the grm section of the .as file
    AsremlGrms
    Class to hold the list of Grm sections to write in the .as file.
    AsremlModel
    The Class AsremlModel is used to define an ASREML command file.
    AsremlModelBlup
    The Class AsremlModel is used to define an ASREML command file for multivariate blup jobs.
    AsremlPrediction  
    AsremlPredictions  
    AsremlQualifier
    The Class Qualifier is used to define qualifier in the ASREML command file
    AsremlQualifiers
    The Class Qualifiers is used to store a collection of AsremlQualifier s.
    AsremlRandomEffect
    The Class AsremlRandomEffect is used to store a collection of AsremlRandomEffectStructures.
    AsremlRandomEffects
    The Class AsremlRandomEffects is used to store a collection of AsremlRandomEffect s.
    AsremlRandomEffectStructure
    The Class AsremlRandomEffectStructure is used to define a random effect variance structure in the ASREML command file.
    AsremlShellScript
    Class to create a unix command to run the Asreml.sh executable program.
    AsremlTab
    The Class AsremlTab is used to define how tabulation should be performed in ASREML.
    AsremlTabs
    The Class AsremlTabs is used to store a collection of AsremlTab s.
